<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> First Letter - which is sent to Mirabor.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
Dear Sister Mirabor,<br>
<br>
Please let me know what I can do to help.  I have many books on spirituality but I must confess, I have little real experience.  I will seek the wisdom and guidence of Mithaniel Marr this evening on this matter.<br>
<br>
Sincerly,<br>
Krystarn<br>
