<br>
She stepped outside and gazed at the clear sky. Quickly calculating the phase of the moon, she made a decision. The time for new beginnings was the New Moon. On that night, they would gather. On that night, the Healing would be done.<br>
<br>
((ooc: That makes it Sunday, October 6th. Probably early evening. Kerra Isle [next to Toxxulia Forest] at the campfire.))<br>
<br>
She hurried back inside to send messages informing the healers of her decision.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub101.ezboard.com/fcircleofsistersfrm25.showPrevMessage?topicID=302.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub101.ezboard.com/fcircleofsistersfrm25.showNextMessage?topicID=302.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fcircleofsistersfrm25.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=302.topic&index=5><img src=http://www.circleofsisters.net/addreplycos.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fcircleofsistersfrm25.threadControl?topicID=302.topic><img src=http://www.soulcadre.com/Image10.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fcircleofsistersfrm25.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=302.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fcircleofsistersfrm25.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=302.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub101.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="circleofsistersfrm1">General Discussion<option value="circleofsistersfrm25">Roleplaying Only<option value="circleofsistersfrm11">The Market<option value="circleofsistersfrm44">Announcements<option value="circleofsistersfrm36">Raid Forum<option value="circleofsistersfrm43">Gallery<option value="circleofsistersfrm28">The Combined Council Place<option value="circleofsistersfrm4">Access and Title Requests<option va